      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I have spent a ridiculous number of hours inside presentation software. Clicking through slide masters, adjusting text boxes by two pixels, exporting, re-exporting, and then realizing the font broke on my client's machine. You know the drill.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
