      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Gamma ended that cycle for me.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you have not tried it yet, Gamma (gamma.app) is an AI-powered platform that turns a simple text prompt into polished presentations, documents, websites, social media content, and even graphics — in under sixty seconds. No design skills required. No template Tetris. Just your idea, rendered beautifully.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "But \"what is it\" is only half the question. The real question is: ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "what can you actually do with it?",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Below, I walk through seven concrete, real-world use cases where Gamma absolutely shines. Whether you are a solo founder, a teacher, a consultant, or part of a marketing team, at least one of these will hit home.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
