      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Pitch Decks That Close Deals (Not Bore Investors)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I once watched a founder spend three weeks on a pitch deck. Three weeks. He had the numbers, the story, the traction — everything was there. But the slides looked like a college group project from 2014.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Gamma fixes this in minutes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You type something like: *\"Create a 12-slide pitch deck for a B2B SaaS startup in the logistics space. Series A, $2M ARR, targeting enterprise shippers.\"* Gamma generates a full deck with structured slides — problem, solution, market size, traction, team, financials, ask — complete with clean layouts, suggested visuals, and logical flow.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The best part? You can edit everything inline. Swap a chart, rewrite a headline, adjust the color palette. It is not a static template. It is a living document that adapts to your input.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I have personally used Gamma to build investor decks in under twenty minutes that looked like they came from a $5,000 design agency. No exaggeration.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
