      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Consultants, agencies, freelancers — this one is for you.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every week, you probably send out proposals, status reports, or deliverables to clients. The content is solid, but packaging it takes forever. You open a blank document, stare at it, start typing, second-guess the structure, Google \"proposal template,\" download something ugly, and spend an hour reformatting.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Gamma lets you skip the entire formatting phase. Paste in your bullet points or rough notes, tell Gamma the format you want (proposal, quarterly report, project brief), and it delivers a polished, professional document. Clean typography. Logical sections. Ready to send.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One agency owner I spoke with told me she cut her proposal turnaround from four hours to forty minutes. That is not a productivity hack — that is a business advantage.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/gamma-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For practical strategies on getting the most out of this workflow, see our ",
