      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Teachers and trainers get a raw deal when it comes to content creation tools. Most \"education-friendly\" platforms are either clunky LMS add-ons or bare-bones slide editors that look like they were built in 2008.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
