      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Gamma is different. It understands educational content natively.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Imagine typing: *\"Create a 15-slide lesson on photosynthesis for 10th-grade biology students, with key vocabulary highlighted and a summary quiz at the end.\"* Gamma produces exactly that — visually engaging slides with age-appropriate language, clear section breaks, and even interactive elements you can toggle on or off.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "University professors use it for lecture decks. Corporate trainers use it for onboarding modules. Online course creators use it to build entire module presentations in an afternoon.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform also exports to PDF and Google Slides, so you are never locked in. Build in Gamma, present however you want.",
            "marks": []
          }
