      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Content marketers, listen up. You know the drill: write the blog post, then create a LinkedIn carousel, then make an Instagram graphic, then draft a Twitter thread, then repurpose for a newsletter. By the time you have distributed one piece of content across five platforms, half your day is gone.",
