        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The output is visually polished — not the clip-art-tier graphics you get from most free tools. The typography is clean, the layouts are modern, and the content structure actually makes sense for each platform's format.",
            "marks": []
