      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every growing team faces the same problem: institutional knowledge lives in Slack threads, random Google Docs, and people's heads. When someone leaves, critical information walks out the door with them.",
