      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Gamma is an excellent tool for building structured internal documentation. Onboarding guides, process runbooks, SOPs, meeting notes templates, team wikis — you name it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The AI helps you structure information logically. You give it rough notes or a brain dump, and it organizes them into clear, scannable sections with headings, bullet points, and summaries. The output looks professional enough to share with the whole team without embarrassment.",
            "marks": []
          }
