      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Several startups I know have replaced their Notion wikis with Gamma docs for client-facing documentation, simply because the output looks better and requires zero formatting effort.",
